~ rhythms — scrolls of time and repetition
~ invoke "rhythms" to bring these incantations into your scroll.

~ a steady pulse: burn a tone n times, each held for one beat
incant pulse takes f, n
  repeat n
    burn f for 0.25
    drift 0.25
    breathe
  end
end

~ a heartbeat: two quick tones, then rest
incant heartbeat takes f
  burn f for 0.1
  drift 0.1
  burn f for 0.1
  drift 0.5
  breathe
end
